The evidence with the title 'Poll: Americans overwhelmingly like Obamacare more than Trumpcare ' says May 16, 2017  ... A new poll shows Americans aren't big fans of the new GOP healthcare bill and even like the old system better.  ... Poll: Americans overwhelmingly like Obamacare more than Trumpcare  ... In terms of simple approval, only 25 percent of those in the poll supported the AHCA while 52 percent opposed it. 
